Cell.Text: In the name of House Redoran, I'm ordering you to stay where you are!
One moment... you look familiar.
Stop right there... where have I seen you before?
The only mistake here belongs to you. You're a wanted man and there's no way I'm letting you walk away.
The only mistake here belongs to you. You're a wanted woman and there's no way I'm letting you walk away.
There's no mistake. You've committed crimes against the Dunmer people of Solstheim, and in the name of House Redoran it's time to face justice.
What in the name of Azura...?
In House Redoran's name, I order you to stop!
You've committed crimes against the Dunmer people of Solstheim. What say you in your defense?
[S] G|Very well, you're free to go. Next time you might not be so lucky.

Node.Caption: DLC2DGCrimePersuade: Any chance I could talk you into overlooking this? (Persuade)

Cell.Text: [S] Wise choice. Now come along with us. After we confiscate any stolen goods, you'll be free to go. After you pay the fine, of course.
[S] Good enough. I'll just remove any stolen goods on you, and then you're free to go.

Node.Caption: DLC2DGCrimePayFine: You caught me. I'll pay off my bounty. ( gold)

Cell.Text: [S] G|I suppose I can overlook it for now, but you better keep your hands clean or I'll come after you again... you got that?
[S] G|You're lucky the bounty on you is so low, otherwise I'd be hauling you to the Bulwark myself. Get out of my sight.

Node.Caption: DLC2DGCrimeNeverMind: I don't have time for this. Do you?

Cell.Text: [S] Right then! Off to the Bulwark with you.

Node.Caption: DLC2DGGoToJail: I submit. Take me to jail.

Cell.Text: [S] G|Good. I've been itching for a fight.
[S] G|If death is what you seek... I'll be happy to oblige!
[S] G|Then in House Redoran's name, you'll get your wish!
[S] G|Solstheim has no use for your kind!

Node.Caption: DLC2DGCrimeResistArrest: I'd rather die than go to prison!

Cell.Text: [S] G|Well, I suppose I could forget that I saw you this time.
How about I pay you some gold and you look the other way? ( gold)
[S] All right, just keep it quiet. I warn you though, there's still a price on your head. Next guard you run into might not be so... agreeable.

Node.Caption: DLC2DGCrimeBribe: I'm with the Guild. How about you look the other way? ( gold)
